    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single below-required factor (Test conditions, achieved level 2 vs. required level 3) is mitigated by the high consistency of FEA predictions with experimental data across both laboratories and by the conservative nature of quasi-static loading relative to in vivo cyclic loading. Overall credibility is sufficient to support the Medium model risk level and Medium decision consequence. Package accepted for regulatory submission.",
